<h2>Managing cookies&nbsp;</h2>
<p>You have options when it comes to which cookies your browser will use.&nbsp;</p>
<p>You can set your browser to:&nbsp;</p>
<ul>
<li>allow all cookies&nbsp;</li>
<li>allow only 'trusted' sites to send them&nbsp;</li>
<li>accept only those cookies from websites you are currently using&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
<p>We recommend that you do not block all cookies because parts of the website rely on them to work properly.&nbsp;</p>
<p>The way to manage your cookies depends on which browser you are using.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
